        "product_description": {
            "value": "The GEAR AID Outerwear Care Kit is a complete cleaning and waterproofing system designed to keep your GORE-TEX fabric and technical outerwear performing like new. This easy-to-use kit includes Revivex Pro Cleaner and Revivex Wash-In Water Repellent, working together to clean, restore breathability, and protect your gear from water, dirt, and stains. The Pro Cleaner gently removes contaminants that can compromise performance, while the Wash-In Water Repellent renews the durable water repellent (DWR) finish, helping moisture bead and roll off the surface. Ideal for jackets, pants, and other waterproof-breathable garments, this care system extends the life of your favorite outerwear so it continues to look great and keep you dry and comfortable in the outdoors.",
